#home_intro.container
  .full_width
    %h2 What’s your solution? Make it matter even more
    %p.bold Do you successfully work with refugees, but you lack the resources to scale your approach globally?
    %p.bold Do you have a solution in the private sector that could work for refugees, but you don’t know how?
    %p GIZ gives you the opportunity to work with our network of development experts, designers, and entrepreneurs to scale your solution and make it matter to people that need it most. Win a trip to Rwandaa and prototype your solution in a GIZ Innovation Lab.
    .accordion
      .accord-single
        .accord-toggle
          .bold.red
            =fa_icon "plus-circle"
            Why you should participate…
        .accord-cont
          %p.bold.low_margin Receive funding to improve and scale your solution 
          %p The selected solutions receive up to 10,000 Euros to be developed further, adapted to the local context and implemented in Rwanda. 
          %p.bold.low_margin Access the expertise of the GIZ network 
          %p You can benefit from the expertise and support of GIZ, Germany’s development agency and its network of experts from leading global and local organisations. 
          %p.bold.low_margin Go on a learning journey to Rwanda 
          %p Throughout the project you will collaborate closely with a team of expert designers and development experts to push your ideas and adapt them locally. In a one week design workshop in Rwanda you will prototype your idea working with local experts and members of the refugee and host communities. All travel cost will be covered! 
          %p.bold.low_margin Gain some fame 
          %p You have the chance to see your solution promoted through media, partners and GIZ channels.


